LA  1  DP2            DP2
PA   1   1.000000e+001 EIN   
PA   2   1.000000e+001 M     
PA   3   1.000000e+002 PK    
PA   4   1.000000e+001 PCF   
PA   5   0.000000e+000 PF    
NS       2               NUMBER OF STATE VARIABLES
IN       1               NUMBER OF ADDITIONAL INTEGRAL VARIABLES
ND       0               NUMBER OF DUMMY VARIABLES
PT  1   0.000000e+000    SIMULATION STRAT TIME
PT  2   1.000000e+001    SIMULATION END TIME
PT  3   1.000000e-005    SIMULATION TIME WIDTH
NO         1000               NUMBER OF OUTPUT TIMES
OP            1               NUMBER OF OUTPUT VARIABLES
END
